description: Works to trees in the Enfield Lock Conservation Area- 1x robinia (T3):lift crown to 3m above ground level, 1x robinia (TG2):lift crown to 2.5m above ground level, 1x goat willow(T5):lift crown to 4m over road way, prune off unit by up to 2m to allow 2m clearance, 1x elder (TG3): prune all back by 2.5m to boundary fence line, 1x rowan(T7):fell to ground level, 1x cherry (T8): lift crown to 2.5m above ground level, prune off unit by up to 2m to allow 2m clearance.
